message.body: Ready as I'll ever be! My roommates are great, very good with intention and being centered so they're good influences. Im happy and excited
I'm so happy for you and I wish I could have been there for you... Connection is all I want and you're the one missy.
:) how was your weekend? And Katie?
It was really good. We had a really honest conversation and it was mostly about me. She just wants me to be honest about how I react to her personality.
I'm curious to hear more. Are you free tonight?
I'm not right now because I'm out with abt kids...
Mmm ok. Is it easy to explain a little more?
Yeah, what do u want to know?
Well how did it relate specifically to the situation?
